data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Virginia Beach! This beautiful townhome offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. This home features, a spacious layout with ample natural light, open-concept living and dining area, great for entertaining, Cozy fireplace, Updated kitchen with sleek countertops, Private patio, fully fenced, made for outdoor dining or relaxation, two generously sized bedrooms, each with its own ensuite bathroom and convenient half bathroom on the main level for guests. Come see it today!
